If you are using a complex object or array as context key, this method will always return `true` and thus setting the same context results in a context key change event:

https://github.com/microsoft/vscode/blob/1e4040626bc797bdf2156fa4d405d8b6ec42f153/src/vs/platform/contextkey/browser/contextKeyService.ts#L39-L46

